import React from 'react'
import { Card } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const src1 = '/friends.jpg'
const src2 = '/restaurant.jpg'
const src3 = '/map.png'
const Container = () => (
  <Card.Group itemsPerRow={4}>
    <Card color='red' image={src1} />
    <Card color='orange' image={src2} />
    <Card color='yellow' image={src3} />
  </Card.Group>
)

export default Container
